175
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obey the warnings in the science classroom
and find it?</font>

176
00:08:17,910 --> 00:08:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The warnings in the science classroom...</font>

177
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anna, over here!</font>

178
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

179
00:08:25,050 --> 00:08:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at this!</font>

180
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:27,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire.</font>

181
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's about fire.</font>

182
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:32,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obey the warnings.
Maybe it's about this?</font>

183
00:08:32,930 --> 00:08:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes... Many experiments use fire,
so we have to be careful.</font>

184
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:42,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If a big flame comes up,
you have to put it out.</font>

185
00:08:42,230 --> 00:08:43,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put out the fire.</font>

186
00:08:46,070 --> 00:08:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should put out this fire.</font>

187
00:08:48,450 --> 00:08:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fire on the poster? How?</font>

188
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like this!</font>

189
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Huh? This part too?
-Whoa! A key!</font>

190
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hooray!</font>

191
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not bad.</i></font>

192
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But can you solve the next puzzle?</i></font>

193
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikuru!</font>

194
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

195
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll solve any mystery!</font>

196
00:09:19,890 --> 00:09:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Again?</font>

197
00:09:23,810 --> 00:09:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on... This classroom is...</font>

198
00:09:27,690 --> 00:09:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The music classroom?</font>

199
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MUSIC CLASSROOM, PASSAGE, SCIENCE CLASROOM</font>

200
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:40,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first one was the science classroom.</font>

201
00:09:40,710 --> 00:09:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now we're in the music classroom.</font>

202
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:45,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're being transported
to different places.</font>

203
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Escape...</i></font>

204
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A key is needed to open the door.</i></font>

205
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Press the keys.</i></font>

206
00:09:51,970 --> 00:09:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Press the keys? What does that mean?</font>

207
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's interesting.
What are those five lines?</font>

208
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Five lines in the music classroom...</font>

209
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:03,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be a staff?</font>

210
00:10:03,350 --> 00:10:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that thing that music is written on!</font>

211
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it is, then the keyhole represents
notes. Align this on the staff, and...</font>

212
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:15,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do, mi, so. The key is do, mi, so!</font>

213
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how can we
press the key of do, mi, so?</font>

214
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure...</font>

215
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like I almost got it...</font>

216
00:10:26,290 --> 00:10:29,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is the do, mi, so key?</font>

217
00:10:29,210 --> 00:10:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There! The piano!</font>

218
00:10:31,210 --> 00:10:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the piano?</font>

219
00:10:32,420 --> 00:10:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Specifically, that part of the piano!
The keyboard!</font>

220
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}KEYBOARD</font>

221
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You write keyboard like this, right?</font>

222
00:10:37,930 --> 00:10:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first part can be read as "key."</font>

223
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}KEY</font>

224
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! So that's what
pressing the keys means!</font>

225
00:10:43,430 --> 00:10:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We play it on the keyboard!</font>

226
00:10:45,650 --> 00:10:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those notes we saw!
They're in a line like balls on a skewer.</font>

227
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CHORD</font>

228
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a chord, and you take
different notes on the keyboard,</font>

229
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}DO MI SO</font>

230
00:10:56,660 --> 00:10:58,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and play them at the same time!</font>

231
00:10:58,950 --> 00:11:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, using the piano...</font>

232
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We play the do, mi, so chord!</font>

233
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Alright!
-Mikuru, you're amazing!</font>

234
00:11:10,210 --> 00:11:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to take piano lessons!</font>

235
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They got it!</font>

236
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goemon, you're having fun.</font>

237
00:11:17,010 --> 00:11:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weren't you watching
for the fairy's power?</font>

238
00:11:19,970 --> 00:11:23,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's about time for my entrance.</font>

239
00:11:23,180 --> 00:11:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not listening.</font>

240
00:11:24,770 --> 00:11:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just watch.</font>

241
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

242
00:11:28,650 --> 00:11:30,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, ready for the next key!</font>

243
00:11:30,730 --> 00:11:31,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Escape...</i></font>

244
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A key is needed to open the door.</i></font>

245
00:11:34,990 --> 00:11:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have the key.</i></font>

246
00:11:37,070 --> 00:11:38,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has it?</font>

247
00:11:38,660 --> 00:11:41,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess we have to find
that Goemon character.</font>

248
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:46,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's simple! We just check every place
we think he might hide!</font>

249
00:11:43,660 --> 00:11:46,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LENDING DESK</font>

250
00:11:46,210 --> 00:11:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, I almost forgot!</i></font>

251
00:11:48,580 --> 00:11:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This time you have one minute to solve it!</i></font>

252
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you don't find me
within the time limit, it's game over.</i></font>

253
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Huh?!
-That's not fair!</font>

254
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Start!</i></font>

255
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-What are we gonna do?</font>

256
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:04,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know! The Pre-Kit!</font>

257
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah!</font>

258
00:12:09,190 --> 00:12:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Open!</font>

259
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pre-Kit Mirror Loupe!</font>

260
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

261
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's the Precures'
detective toolset, the Pre-Kit!</i></font>

262
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jett-senpai says with the Mirror Loupe
we won't miss any important clues!</font>

263
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gold-star discovery!</font>

264
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the shape of Goemon's sandal print!</font>

265
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's one way to use it. Fine.</i></font>

266
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They call me the master of hide-and-seek.
Will they be able to find me?</i></font>

267
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The tracks stop here.</font>

268
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are there any more?</font>

269
00:12:46,930 --> 00:12:48,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We only have ten seconds left!</font>

270
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

271
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:52,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-What about behind this bookshelf?</font>

272
00:12:56,860 --> 00:12:58,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We found him!</font>

273
00:13:00,740 --> 00:13:02,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job, Star Detectives.</font>

274
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imagine beating me at hide and seek!</font>

275
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kudos to you!</font>

276
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We cleared the library puzzle!</font>

277
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:14,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">HOME EC CLASSROOM</font>

278
00:13:14,380 --> 00:13:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">KNIT A KEY</font>

279
00:13:23,850 --> 00:13:25,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">ART CLASSROOM</font>

280
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

281
00:13:37,190 --> 00:13:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The gym?</font>

282
00:13:38,650 --> 00:13:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This was our first location.</font>

283
00:13:40,860 --> 00:13:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the final puzzle.</i></font>

284
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Escape...</i></font>

285
00:13:44,990 --> 00:13:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Choose the correct door!</i></font>

286
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To go forward you must go back.
Create a path from nothing.</i></font>

287
00:13:52,170 --> 00:13:54,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To go forward, go back?</font>

288
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's a hint.</font>

289
00:14:01,090 --> 00:14:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A mark on the door?</font>

290
00:14:05,090 --> 00:14:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That one, too!</font>

291
00:14:07,260 --> 00:14:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Each of the five doors has one.</font>

292
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A circle, triangle, star,
music note, and an X.</font>

293
00:14:14,980 --> 00:14:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think they're hints
to help solve the puzzle.</font>

294
00:14:17,610 --> 00:14:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those marks,
and the meaning of the clue...</font>

295
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:24,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you're stuck, go back to the beginning!</i></font>

296
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said that before, didn't you?</font>

297
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should look back on
the other puzzles we solved!</font>

298
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

299
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}GYM, SCIENCE CLASSROOM, MUSIC CLASSROOM
LIBRARY, HOME EC CLASSROOM, ART CLASSROOM</font>

300
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rooms we passed through,
and the marks.</font>

301
00:14:35,250 --> 00:14:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We solved a puzzle in the music room,
so maybe it's the note?</font>

302
00:14:39,250 --> 00:14:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember what Goemon said.</font>

303
00:14:42,340 --> 00:14:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CREATE A PATH FROM NOTHING</font>

304
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Create a path from nothing.</font>

305
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that's important.</font>

306
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A path...</font>

307
00:14:48,350 --> 00:14:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a trick maze.
To get through the maze, we solve puzzles.</font>

308
00:14:54,890 --> 00:14:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got it!</font>

309
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

310
00:14:57,400 --> 00:15:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the places we passed through!
We should connect them!</font>

311
00:15:00,730 --> 00:15:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}GYM</font>

312
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, the gym.</font>

313
00:15:02,650 --> 00:15:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SCIENCE CLASSROOM, MUSIC CLASSROOM
LYBRARY</font>

314
00:15:02,820 --> 00:15:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then the science classroom,
music classroom, library.</font>

315
00:15:06,820 --> 00:15:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Home ec classroom, art classroom,
and back to the gym.</font>

316
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}HOME EC CLASSROOM, ART CLASSROOM
GYM</font>

317
00:15:13,830 --> 00:15:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should mean something...</font>

318
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Oh! We overlap them!
-Huh?</font>

319
00:15:27,430 --> 00:15:29,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The maps!
First floor and second floor!</font>

320
00:15:30,140 --> 00:15:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Separately, they look like nothing.</font>

321
00:15:32,810 --> 00:15:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put them together, and the paths join up!</font>

322
00:15:42,610 --> 00:15:43,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see!</font>

323
00:15:43,820 --> 00:15:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the answer!</font>

324
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the door with the star!</font>

325
00:15:48,950 --> 00:15:50,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Let's go!
-Yeah!</font>

326
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we out?</font>

327
00:15:58,880 --> 00:16:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done!</font>

328
00:16:01,090 --> 00:16:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't learn much about the fairy,
but I'll take the Makoto Jewel!</font>

329
00:16:08,430 --> 00:16:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lies, envelop!</font>

330
00:16:11,300 --> 00:16:14,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Hanninda!</font>

331
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

332
00:16:23,610 --> 00:16:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-The cherry blossom tree!
-Mikuru, let's go!</font>

333
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Open!</font>

334
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jewel Cure Watch!</font>

335
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Precure! Wake-up Time!</font>

336
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">3! Discover!</font>

337
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">6! And face one another!</font>

338
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">9! We are the miraculous duo!</font>

339
00:17:24,670 --> 00:17:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spin around!</font>

340
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And finish off cutely!</font>

341
00:17:52,610 --> 00:17:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gold-star closing the case on any mystery!</font>

342
00:17:55,870 --> 00:17:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Star Detective Cure Answer!</font>

343
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jumping towards smiles
with layered reasoning!</font>

344
00:18:04,130 --> 00:18:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Star Detective Cure Mystique!</font>

345
00:18:11,340 --> 00:18:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Star Detective Precure!</font>

346
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you my answer!</font>

347
00:18:18,930 --> 00:18:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

348
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:27,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nin! Da!</font>

349
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

350
00:18:34,660 --> 00:18:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mystique Reflection!</font>

351
00:18:40,410 --> 00:18:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cunning!</font>

352
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get smothered in cherry blossom petals!</font>

353
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Mystique!
-I've got this!</font>

354
